(476, '_transient_wc_upgrade_notice_2.2.4', '<div class="wc_plugin_upgrade_notice">2.3.0 is a major update so it is important that you make backups, test extensions and your theme prior to updating, and ensure extensions are 2.3 compatible. Developers should catch up with <a href="http://develop.woothemes.com/">develop.woothemes.com</a> to see what has been happening in core.</div> ', 'no'),
