anri.syaiful">Anri Syaiful</a></p>', 'Hidayat Nur Wahid Sebut Koalisi Jokowi-JK Mulai Goyah', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-19 11:10:26', '2014-09-19 11:10:26', '', 5, 'http://128.199.195.225/hnw/?p=6', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
